        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【CES2025】ASUS ROG Flow Z13 电竞平板， AMD Ryzen AI MAX+ 395 处理器、最高 32 GB RAM</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/asus-rog-flow-z13/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=asus-rog-flow-z13</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/asus-rog-flow-z13/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 13:17:10 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[asus]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Asus ROG]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CES2025]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286028</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>ASUS ROG 在 CES 2025 展示了全新升级版的 Flow Z13 (2025)，将游戏性能与便携设计结合至极致，配备强劲硬件与突破性设计，为玩家提供顶尖的游戏体验。Flow Z13（2025）外观未作出重大改动，但在提供丰富 I/O 连接埠的基础上新增专属 Command Center 控制键。硬体方面采用了次世代 AMD Ryzen AI MAX+ 395 处理器。此外萤幕从 3 年前的 FHD 120Hz 升级至 2.5K QHD 180Hz，并引入康宁 Gorilla Glass DXC 技术，进一步提升耐用性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286094" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rogflowz13-1-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rogflowz13-1-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rogflowz13-1-scaled.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rogflowz13-1-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286031" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_2-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_2-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_2-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_2.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></h3><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286045" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_10-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_10-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_10-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_10.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286042" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_8-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_8-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_8-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_8.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">ROG Flow Z13 2025 可配备最新 AMD Ryzen™ AI MAX+ 395 处理器，具备 16 核心 32 线程，基本时脉达到 3.0GHz，为多工处理与高效能应用提供强大支持。此外 AMD XDNA NPU 提供高达 50TOPS 的 AI 处理能力，进一步提升系统效能。</p><p data-pm-slice="1 1 []"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286035" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_3-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_3-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_3-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_3.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">ROG Flow Z13 配备 ROG Nebula 霓真技术电竞萤幕，尺寸为 13.4 吋，提供 2.5K (2560 x 1600, WQXGA) 解像度与 16:10 长宽比。萤幕采用光面设计，支援 100% DCI-P3 广色域，具备 180Hz 更新率与 Adaptive-Sync 技术，并通过 Pantone 认证及 Dolby Vision HDR 支援，带来极致的画面表现。</p><p data-pm-slice="1 1 []"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286093" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rogflowz13-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rogflowz13-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rogflowz13-scaled.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rogflowz13-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p data-pm-slice="1 1 []"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286041" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_7-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_7-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_7-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_7.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;" data-pm-slice="1 1 []">▲萤幕尺寸为 13.4 吋</p><p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">ROG Flow Z13 内置 70Wh 大容量电池，支援长时间续航。I/O 连接埠方面，ROG Flow Z13 提供 1 个 3.5mm 音源插孔、1 个 HDMI 2.1 、1 个 USB 3.2 Gen 2 Type-A（数据传输速度可达 10Gbps）、2 个 USB 4 Type-C（支援 DisplayPort 和电力传输，数据传输速度可达 40Gbps），以及 1 个 microSD 卡插槽（UHS-II），充分满足用户的连接需求。同时，装置支援最新的 Wi-Fi 7 技术，让玩家随时随地保持稳定连线。</p><p data-pm-slice="1 1 []"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286039" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_6-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_6-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_6-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_6.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;" data-pm-slice="1 1 []"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286043" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_9-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_9-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_9-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_9.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;" data-pm-slice="1 1 []">▲键盘部分采用背光巧克力键盘，支援 1-Zone RGB 灯效</p><h3></h3><p>ASUS 尚未公布 ROG Flow Z13 的具体上市日期。预计搭载 Ryzen AI Max 390 处理器的版本售价将约为 2,000 美元（约港币 15,560.28 元），而搭载 Ryzen AI Max+ 395 的版本起价为 2,200 美元（约港币 17,116.30 元）。</p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
