        <item>
            <title>【CES2025】香港创科 VIT 获 CES 大奖，三轴微型稳定器提升智能电话相机稳定度</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/mgs-2/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mgs-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/mgs-2/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 12:37:07 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[数码相机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CES2025]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[相机防手震]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286208</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>香港创科企业在美国拉斯维加斯举行的 CES 2025 展览中再创佳绩，当中 Vista Innotech（VIT）的三轴微型稳定器（Micro Gimbal Stabilizer, MGS）于影像技术类别中夺得创新奖，成为大中华地区首个获此殊荣的企业。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286209" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h28-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h28-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h28-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1286220" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010984240-694x479.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="479" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010984240-694x479.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010984240-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>VIT 的三轴 MGS 技术以其精巧设计及卓越性能脱颖而出。产品仅有方糖大小，重量为传统三轴稳定器的三分之一，体积更缩小至十分之一，具 ±8° 的防手震补偿角度，使曝光时间延长至 16 倍，同时生产成本更低。该技术已获超过 110 项专利保护，应用范围涵盖穿戴式相机、安全头盔及机械人装置。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286211" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h28-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h28-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h28-2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286210" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h28-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h28-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h28-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286213" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/threeaxismicrogimbal-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/threeaxismicrogimbal-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/threeaxismicrogimbal.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>VIT 行政总裁麦启邦博士表示，作为大中华首间获得 CES 创新奖影像技术殊荣的企业，这不仅肯定了 VIT 对技术创新及品质的追求，亦展现了香港企业于全球科技舞台上的潜力。MGS 亦曾获 2024 年日内瓦发明展银奖及第二届城市创科挑战大奖。</p><h3></h3><figure id="attachment_1286214" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1286214" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1286214" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010983410-694x410.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="410" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010983410-694x410.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010983410-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1286214" class="wp-caption-text">▲在 CES 2025 这个三幅微型影像稳定器获得创新奖</figcaption></figure><p>资料来源：Unwire.hk, <a href="https://www.ces.tech/ces-innovation-awards/2025/three-axis-micro-gimbal-stabilizer/">CES</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
