            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Kodak 与 Barbie 联手推出 Barbie x Kodak Printomatic，即影即有相机结合复古与创新设计，吸引年轻用户与 Barbie 迷关注。相机提供 500 万像素解像度及 ZINK 无墨技术，打印防污、防水及防撕裂的 2×3 吋贴背相片。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286201" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-7-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-7-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-7-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286188" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286199" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/barbiexkodaknews-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/barbiexkodaknews-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/barbiexkodaknews.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>相机采用轻巧设计，方便携带，并以 Barbie 经典粉红色包装，外型亮眼又实用。内置自动闪光灯与自动对焦功能，让拍摄者无需经验亦能捕捉清晰影像。相片除即时打印外，相机还支援 MicroSD 卡储存，方便用户保存数码档案。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286189" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286190" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286191" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-3-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>此相机既能作日常拍摄用，也适合成为收藏品。对于喜爱 Barbie 主题产品的用户而言，这款即影即有相机同时带来怀旧趣味及现代拍摄体验。</p><h4>规格</h4><ul><li><strong>解像度</strong>：500 万像素数码相机</li><li><strong>打印技术</strong>：ZINK 无墨打印，2×3 吋贴背相片</li><li><strong>功能</strong>：自动闪光灯、自动对焦、MicroSD 存储支援</li><li><strong>设计</strong>：Barbie 经典粉红造型</li></ul><h4>售价与供应</h4><p>Barbie x Kodak Printomatic 现已推出，售价 £84.99（约港币 HK$663）。</p><br /><b>
