        <item>
            <title>【CES2025】LG UltraGear 可弯曲电竞荧幕抢镜，用家一个指令荧幕马上流畅变弯</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/lg-ultragear-5k2k/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lg-ultragear-5k2k</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/lg-ultragear-5k2k/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 12:06:46 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[LG UltraGear]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286170</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>LG 在 CES 2025 展示他们的最新显示技术，推出全球首款 5K2K 解像度可弯曲 OLED 显示器 45GX990A，并赢得三项创新大奖，包括备受瞩目的「最佳创新奖」。这款 UltraGear GX9 系列具备的弯曲屏幕设计，可以随用家需要拉直，或变弯曲（详细效果可看下面的影片），还融入多项针对游戏玩家的创新功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286184" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgultrageargx945gx99-694x422.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="422" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgultrageargx945gx99-694x422.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgultrageargx945gx99.jpg 800w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286174" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h53-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h53-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h53-2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><p>LG UltraGear 45GX990A 是一款尺寸达 45 吋、21:9 比例的 OLED 游戏显示器，拥有超高 5K2K 解像度（5,120 x 2,160）。用户可透过按钮实现屏幕从平面至 900R 曲率之间的自动转换，适合游戏玩家在沉浸式游戏与工作应用之间灵活切换。展示期间，LG 提供了一套红色按钮操控装置，让参观者体验这款屏幕弯曲与平展切换的流畅效果。未来消费版产品将搭载遥控器进行操作。</p><h3></h3><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286173" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h53-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h53-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h53-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286175" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h53-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h53-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h53-3-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><p>这款显示器采用了 LG 最新 WOLED 技术，提供高亮度、深黑色、丰富色彩及最佳曲率，为游戏玩家打造更逼真的画面。同时产品通过低蓝光认证，减少长时间游戏时的眼部负担。内置的 Dual Mode 功能支持用户一键切换多种画面比例及更新率配置，适应不同类型的游戏与内容需求。</p><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286185" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgultrageargx945gx95-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgultrageargx945gx95-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgultrageargx945gx95.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="VID_20250108_102048" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1045315936?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script><br />
资料来源：LG, Unwire.hk</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/lg-ultragear-5k2k/notebook/">【CES2025】LG UltraGear 可弯曲电竞荧幕抢镜，用家一个指令荧幕马上流畅变弯</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
