        <item>
            <title>【CES2025】Lenovo ThinkBook Plus Gen6，荧幕可卷动、售价 3499 美元起</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/lenovo-thinkbook-plus-gen-6/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lenovo-thinkbook-plus-gen-6</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/lenovo-thinkbook-plus-gen-6/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 12:03:41 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CES2025]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[lenovo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Lenovo ThinkBook]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Lenovo ThinkBook Plus Gen6]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286116</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Lenovo 在 CES2025 展示了他们最新的 ThinkBook Plus Gen6，与传统笔记型电脑不同，这款全新登场的 ThinkBook Plus Gen6 配备全球首个可卷曲（rollable）荧幕，据悉将在今年首季度推出，预期售价为 $3,499 美元（约港币 27,223 元）。ThinkBook Plus Gen6 表面上就如一部 14 吋手提电脑，但荧幕可延伸至 16.7 吋，并支援 120 Hz 更新率，用家可以利用更大荧幕灵活办公。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286137" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo5-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo5-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo5-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo5.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲伸延前为 14 吋荧幕</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286138" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo6-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo6-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo6-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo6.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可伸延至 16.7 吋</p><p>ThinkBook Plus Gen6 最具颠覆性的设计是其可卷曲荧幕。这项突破性技术可根据需求灵活扩展，让使用者随时获得更多操作空间，无论是会议中迅速查找资料、展示文件，还是进行创意设计，这款笔记型电脑都能够自如应对。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286119" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo1-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo1-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo1-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo1.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击 F12 旁边按键</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286135" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo4-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo4-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo4-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo4.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家亦可以用手势延伸荧幕</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286124" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo2-580x580.jpeg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo2-580x580.jpeg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo2-144x144.jpeg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo2.jpeg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲即可延伸荧幕</p><p>Lenovo ThinkBook Plus Gen6 使用了前所未见的卷动荧幕，其体积和重量并未比传统手提电脑大或重太多。它重量为 1.63kg，厚度约 1.9cm，保持轻巧与便携性，让使用者随时随地都能拥有极致的工作效率。ThinkBook Plus Gen 6 内置 Intel Core Ultra 7 CPU、最高可达 32 GB RAM 及 1TB SSD。预期 Lenovo 将会在今年第一季推出 ThinkBook Plus Gen 6，以 $3,499 美元的（约港币 27,225.11 元）价格上市。预计它将吸引大量追求创新与高效能的商业专业人士与创意工作者，成为他们办公桌上的新宠。</p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
